Package org.jsweet.transpiler

Class TypeChecker

java.lang.Object
org.jsweet.transpiler.TypeChecker
public class TypeChecker extends Object
This helper class performs extra type checking for the JSweet transpiler (additionally to Java default type checking).

It checks that JSweet authorized APIs are used, and that auxiliary types such as unions are valid.

Author:
Renaud Pawlak, Louis Grignon
